section#who-we-are
  .container.inner-md
    .row.inner-top-xs
      .col-sm-6.inner-right-xs.inner-bottom-xs
        h2 Who we are
        p Hiya Friends,

        p We are Adelina and Dan, two persons passionate about photography and stories. <strong>Remindmetolive</strong> is the way we contribute to the large, funny and poignant human story.

        p Through our photograpy and narative we are sharing a view of the world and remind you that living is not just about being alive, it's about experiencing life through all the little ups and downs that makes it worth living.

        p Have a look around, check out the stories and be a part of this journey. Thank you for supporting us and believing in what we are doing!
      .col-sm-6.inner-left-xs.inner-bottom-xs
        h2 What we do

        p We started the <strong>Remindmetolive</strong> project to share stories of people and places through photography.

        p We believe that a photograph can be really powerful, in the sense that it has the ability to transmit emotions, mood, ideas and messages - all of which are also important elements of story telling.

        p Each and every one of us has a story to tell and by sharing it we can make the workd a better place, as it can inspire other people living now, or the generations to come. No joke, it's been scientifically proven.

        p Let us help you shape and share your story with the world!
